# Lime NLP

Make sure to be in `/lime_llm` (`cd lime_llm`)


## For LIME-LLM
Create the environment
`conda env create -f environment.yml`

Activate the environment
`conda activate lime_nlp`
Conda update
`conda env`

## For Baselines (Isolate LIME local package)

`conda create --name lime_nlp_baselines python=3.12.12 lime==0.2.0.1 shap==0.50.0 captum==0.7.0 python-dotenv transformers==4.57.3 sentence-transformers==5.2.0 --y`


For `script_lime_nlp_baselines_with_seed.py`.

### To remove the env:

`conda env remove --name lime_nlp_baselines --y`